  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That's when we decided it's getting too hot for, for comfort.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we tried to cross the Swiss border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to a town near the Swiss border, where we got in touch with some smugglers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we paid them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they put us in a pickup truck covered with a tarp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we went to the border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at the border, they said, we can't get you across.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there are German patrols.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they are-- with dogs, they'll pick up the scent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It can't be done.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they had the decency of giving us back the money, but we now went back-- excuse me-- we now went back to the South of France.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that time, it became known that, in the Italian zone, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Italians did not permit deportation of Jews to, to Germany.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Perhaps I should open a parenthesis here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When France capitulated, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Germans, as I said, occupied the north.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Italians, who were allies with the Germans, occupied a small sliver of land along the Italian border that went from the Riviera, Nice, all the way to the Swiss border.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It became known that the Italians, although allied with the Germans, would not allow any Jews to be deported from their zone by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So naturally, what ensued was a mass exodus of Jews from the French-occupied zones gravitating towards the Italian.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you could make it without being caught by Germans on the way-- passport controls and identifications and traveling permits and all that-- you were, quote, unquote 'safe.' [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My parents and my brother, Harry, managed to get to that zone.",
      "word_count": 45
    }
  ],
